ng: 4px 10px 4px 5px; width: 162px;\">CHÁO SƯỜN SU SU\r\nSỮA ĐẬU XANH</td>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px 10px 4px 5px; width: 146px;\">CHÁO THỊT ĐẬU ĐỎ\r\nSINH TỐ DƯA HẤU</td>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px 10px 4px 5px; width: 148px;\">CHÁO TRAI HÀNH RĂM\r\nSỮA VINAMILK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"> Thực đơn của bé ở trường Thăng long kid smart Tuần từ 23/09 đến 28/09/2013</span>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 2em; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: normal; color: #f58723; font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: underline;\">MẪU GIÁO :</span></strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </span>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.4em; width: 970px; color: #000000; font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" width=\"970\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px 10px 4px 5px; width: 96px;\"></td>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px 10px 4px 5px; width: 146px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">THỨ 2 ( 23 /09)</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px 10px 4px 5px; width: 146px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outli